	<br>
	<div style="text-align:right;">
		OLIVEIRA, Angela Cristina da Fonseca de<sup>1</sup>; AMARAL, Maycon Rodrigo Cardoso<sup>2</sup>; CORDEIRO, Alanna<sup>3</sup>; MAZUTTI, Kelly<sup>4</sup>; ANDRADE, Carla de<sup>5</sup>; OLIVEIRA, Geovane Rosa de<sup>6</sup>; MELO, Antonio Diego BrandÃo<sup>7</sup>; COSTA, Leandro Batista<sup>8</sup>		<BR>
